00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:23.400
When the head was raised,
when the responsibility was taken
of raising the head,

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:25.440
the brain started growing
in such a way

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:27.880
that it became a pyramid.

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:30.280
