of forces,

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:51.840
by which the resultant force —

00:12:52.040 --> 00:12:54.440
the resultant force —
now, it falls like this,

00:12:54.640 --> 00:12:57.800
goes like that,
the resultant force is like that —

00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:02.640
had two sides: one was this,
another was this.

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:05.800
So the consciousness,
or we can say, the attention,

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:10.160
instead of going inside,
started going out.

00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:13.480
So one part of the resultant
was going outside,

00:13:13.680 --> 00:13:15.840
and that’s how,
when you became a human being,

00:13:16.040 --> 00:13:19.040
your attention went outside.

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:23.840
It’s the human beings only
who have their attention outside.

00:13:24.040 --> 00:13:25.880
Not that the animals don’t have,

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:29.680
but the attention
of human beings are such

00:13:29.880 --> 00:13:32.680
that they create reactions.

00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:36.280
Like, you see something.

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:39.760
Now, I see doctor’s house there,
for example.

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:41.920
