00:14:02.120 --> 00:14:05.080
It’s only the human beings
who reflect.

00:14:05.280 --> 00:14:10.920
And this reflection comes
because of the pyramid-like structure

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:12.560
of the brain.

00:14:12.760 --> 00:14:18.280
