in the brain itself,

00:14:18.480 --> 00:14:22.520
that we start developing
our own ego,

00:14:22.720 --> 00:14:26.280
our own myths,
our own mental projections.

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:29.720
And when we develop
our own mental projections,

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:33.320
this ego starts developing:
“I know,” “What’s wrong?” —

00:14:33.520 --> 00:14:35.560
