as an animal,

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:48.880
and then comes up in the centre.

00:14:49.080 --> 00:14:53.440
That’s how we now become
normal human beings.

00:14:53.640 --> 00:14:57.720
But then we start
increasing our ego.

00:14:57.920 --> 00:15:03.000
