by which we develop our “I-ness”.

00:15:09.640 --> 00:15:13.200
So it is all the happening
that takes place

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:17.240
after we have lifted our head,
raised our head,

00:15:17.440 --> 00:15:20.400
